1. A resource is a fundamental concept in Rest web services.
2. These resources can be Text Files, Html Pages, Images, Videos or Dynamic Business Data
3. A resource in REST is a similar 
    Object in Object Oriented Programming or is like an Entity in a Database.

4. { 
   "id":1, 
   "name":"Mahesh", 
   "profession":"Teacher" 
}

5. <user> 
   <id>1</id> 
   <name>Mahesh</name>
   <profession>Teacher</profession> 
</user> 